'''Kick''' is a 2-cost Basic '''Attack''' card for [[Rook]]. It deals 8 base damage. As a base card '''Kick''' is always part of the available card pool for [[Rook]].

==Upgrades==
After accruing 5 experience '''Kick''' is able to be upgraded.  Like every basic card, '''Kick''' has more than two upgrades, from which it randomly picks 2 you can decide from.
